      • SpatialObjectModel

        protected SpatialObjectModel(java.lang.String name,
                             SpatialObjectTypeModel type,
                             oracle.spatial.geometry.JGeometry geometry)
        Setups object and creates shape for graphic representation from jGeometry. It's protected so that it's not possible to instantiate the class otherwise than by loadFromDB(Long, int, String, SpatialObjectTypeModel, byte[])
        Parameters:
        name - name of spatial object
        type - association to object type (basket, house, path, ...)
        geometry - spatial data
